\begin_layout Enumerate
以 
\begin_inset Formula $x_{i}$
\end_inset

 为中心，对 
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ u_{i+s}\right\} _{s\in S_{i}}$
\end_inset

 作 Taylor 展开：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
u_{i+s}=\sum_{r=0}^{\infty}\left.\frac{\partial^{r}u}{\partial x^{r}}\right|_{i}\frac{(x_{i+s}-x_{i})^{r}}{r!}\equiv\sum_{r=0}^{\infty}\left.\frac{\partial^{r}u}{\partial x^{r}}\right|_{i}\frac{(sh)^{r}}{r!}
\]

\end_inset

这样的展开式有 
\begin_inset Formula $\vert S_{i}\vert$
\end_inset

 个，将它们代入式 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:有限差分：空间格式：一般线性：p 阶导数"

\end_inset

 式即得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left.\frac{\partial^{p}u}{\partial x^{p}}\right|_{i}\approx\sum_{s\in S_{i}}a_{i+s}^{(p)}\underbrace{\sum_{r=0}^{\infty}\left.\frac{\partial^{r}u}{\partial x^{r}}\right|_{i}\frac{(sh)^{r}}{r!}}_{u_{i+s}}=\sum_{r=0}^{\infty}\left.\frac{\partial^{r}u}{\partial x^{r}}\right|_{i}\frac{h^{r}}{r!}\sum_{s\in S_{i}}s^{r}a_{i+s}^{(p)}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

