\sum_{s\in S_{i}}s^{r}a_{i+s}^{(p)}=\frac{r!}{h^{r}}\delta_{p}^{r},\quad r=0,1,\dots,\vert S_{i}\vert-1\label{eq:有限差分：空间格式：Taylor}
